service: my-serverless-app

provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: nodejs20.x
  environment:
    DEBUG: ${env:DEBUG, 0}
    NODE_ENV: ${env:NODE_ENV}
    PORT: ${env:PORT}
    AWSACCESS_KEY_ID: ${env:AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID}
    AWSSECRET_ACCESS_KEY: ${env:AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY}
    AWSREGION: ${env:AWS_REGION}

functions:
  app:
    handler: dist/src/serverless.handler
    events:
      - http:
          method: ANY
          path: /
      - http:
          method: any
          path: /{proxy+}

plugins:
  - serverless-offline
  - serverless-dotenv-plugin
